sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Route as Route: GET /api/categories
    participant Controller as CategoriesController
    participant Model as Category (Model)
    participant DB as Database
    
    Client->>Route: GET /api/categories
    Route->>Controller: __invoke()
    
    Note over Controller: CHANGED: ->with('children')
    
    Controller->>Model: Category::query()->with('children')
    Model->>DB: SELECT * FROM categories<br/>+ children (eager load)
    DB-->>Model: Categories with parent_id
    Model-->>Controller: Collection with relationships loaded
    
    Note over Controller: Eager loading prevents N+1
    
    Controller->>Controller: CategoryResource::collection()
    
    Note over Controller: CHANGED: parent_id field
    Note over Controller: CHANGED: children relationship
    
    Controller-->>Client: JSON with nested categories
    
    Note over Client: Response structure:<br/>{"id":1,"name":"A","parent_id":null,"children":[{"id":2,"name":"B","parent_id":1,"children":[]}]}
